{"type": "article", "id": 52932, "title": "如果行李箱可以自定义颜色、拉链这些细节，你怎么选？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-07T22:54:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 50011, "name": "Miyake Design Studio"}, {"id": 48844, "name": "Estúdio Parrado"}, {"id": 50012, "name": "ROAM"}, {"id": 50013, "name": "Tan Mavitan"}, {"id": 50014, "name": "David Cullimore"}, {"id": 50015, "name": "Vinnay Chhabildas"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 177, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180507215357kDZSMnT16XQoGlYx.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Rotio® Compass by David Cullimore &amp; Vinnay Chhabildas</h3><p>伦敦设计师 David Cullimore 和 Vinnay Chhabildas 推出了取代圆规的画圆工具 Rotio，只需用手指按住中间罗盘，即可用笔旋转画圆。一排多孔，以 5 毫米为增量，更易于确定比例。标准和加长尺寸，直径范围分别为 40-140 毫米和 40-200 毫米 ，满足日常基本作画范围。</p><p>Rotio 罗盘下隐藏橡胶 O 形圈，使 Rotio 稳定不偏移，同时也能够灵活转动，易于精确控制路线。尺身采用可回收材料制成，罗盘则为铝制加工材料，坚固耐用。最近，Rotio® Compass 正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，早鸟价 12 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1342894759/rotio-compass-the-most-intuitive-design-tool\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507215850zpfgbjhFX2NJTrwU.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663462\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507215851hsWzgNCJUycTjEeG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663968\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507215427hnj3eEOy9wkQTDMK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507215427NOVk4KvPoX7z2Q0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507215427xdc4PemEIYKQHoAJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018050721542745BIJgH3dcjb1NXO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Triangle Notebook by Tan Mavitan</h3><p>设计师 Tan Mavitan 创造了一款造型小巧独特的 Triangle Notebook 笔记本。当笔记本合上的时候。它的体积非常小，便于携带，而当它打开的时候，就变成了一个完整的正方形书写区域，丝毫不会影响我们的使用，算得上一款充满创意和惊喜的作品。配色丰富，售价 33 美元，<a href=\"https://trianglenotebook.com/collections/all\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805072159394HXqBU0FiaC6QVWS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805072159393aZHjdenmkKSWGVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507215939sny3N5DR2pCco6Mz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507215939zi8GxnekB261LMRa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805072159391KtvoOQjU3LDHG6s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.785714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507215939wYpAr1z4lM6ZLGuF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.899048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lensball </h3><p>荷兰一家公司推出了一款名为 Lensball 的水晶球，它能将自然风光“装进”其中。你可以把它看作是鱼眼、广角或是微距镜头，在摄影的世界里看见与众不同。这款水晶球由 K9 玻璃制成，其优质的透光度和折光效果能将周围景物一览无余的倒映在其中，是拍摄大片的创意利器。清晰耐刮的材质，提供 60 与 80 毫米两种尺寸。售价 39.99 美元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Lensball-002-80mm/dp/B076BQFDF8/ref=sr_1_3?tag=yankodesign05-20&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1511471374&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=lensball&amp;th=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220017WOZ1gwF79s5Lvp8t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220018JMhFNk4HyeZAtWmr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220018sMRdf6T3401blHvj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220017X3RJk2ENPd7FxG4e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805072200187BsXLPhHwR4kCKeO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220019uAt1Sn4wHbN8kxJO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>First Online Customizable Luggage by ROAM</h3><p>ROAM 是由美国老牌行李箱品牌 TUMI 的两位前任高管离职后创立的一个新品牌，是市场上第一个直接面向消费者、让用户可以按照个人喜好定制的行李箱品牌。行李箱的所有部分，例如外壳、拉链、车线等等，都可以在网上进行定制，配合 10 种不同的色彩搭配，使行李箱的外观更符合用户个性。</p><p>市面上不少亮面外壳行李箱，用一段时间以后，难免会在表面留下刮花的痕迹，但 ROAM 的行李箱采用最高质量的 100% 美国制造的聚碳酸酯制成，所以即使表面被刮花都不会露出底漆，坚固且轻巧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220102u1SxO3lgTX6cBztG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735156\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220102rh5QRulEFKOWIctk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.061719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805072201029qXyNzxoju3PQYkR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805072201029rOcHkDRIwQZqp3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220102Lm7UGhJ5g08poOje.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.530469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220102GVKdNWqPfQnoCv5F.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/roam-introduces-online-customizable-luggage/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Wing Shelving System by Estúdio Parrado</h3><p>圣保罗设计工作室 Estúdio Parrado 推出了一款名为 Wing 的搁架。设计团队认为，不管是会面临搬家的用户，还是家居需求时常发生变化的人，模块化家具都是一个合理的选择，因为它能让你适应任何情况。Wing 是一款可调节的壁挂式搁架，模块化的设计允许用户创造适合自己需求的存储空间，还能结构出不一样的样式。平面搁架由打孔松木制成，支架是由钢切割而成的三角形。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220141VcngEBXDaQKhtGTf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220141yLqkc805CIWj7omu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220142SvpGjoc4NlLbigK0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220142fkHBLIJdpXUD1sMR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220141tTcJwk8rRdq9PVmQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.870313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220142fN2D9XJLb7kYdTIx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.estudioparrado.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Estúdio Parrado</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Table Light by Miyake Design Studio</h3><p>由日本设计师 Kazushige Miyake 创立的 Miyake Design Studio 是日本最受欢迎的工业设计公司之一，他们擅于巧妙地将复杂的功能和简单的审美结合起来，MUJI 也是其长期合作的客户之一。</p><p>这款台灯就是 Kazushige Miyake 的代表作之一，看似极简风格的设计却暗藏可折叠和可充电的功能。关闭的时候，台灯会变成一个精致漂亮的雕塑，顶部还有一个便携式提手。当灯光点亮时，光源可以旋转到不同的角度，便于不同情况下使用它，比如办公室、卧室，甚至是学校。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220222XpzhMPdw2eCjIrVZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220222icxTtQ7IAeqPjVvY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220222phFeaz0Ho4WxdSEf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220222CzLvToShKleNEdcA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220222kb8UyVnBpKxLOovs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180507220222JqUR13bamnr9Gl47.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://admin.qdaily.com/admin/articles/55256/minimalissimo.com\">minimalissimo</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}